      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent grid convergence index study with uncertainty banding required at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed with GCI reported; however temporal discretization error is not separately quantified. Achieved level 3 is one gradation below required."
