      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI must be directly the clinical hemolysis index used in regulatory submission with demonstrated traceability to patient risk metric at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) is computed but conversion to plasma free hemoglobin clinical threshold is not fully documented. Traceability chain to patient harm metric incomplete."
