      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be performed on geometry and flow conditions representative of the specific COU device and patient population at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry, not the specific VAD device geometry. Operating point coverage is partial. Relevance gap is substantial at MRL 5."
