    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors evaluated against MRL 5 requirements for Class III VAD device. Seven factors assessed with achieved levels uniformly below required levels; six factors flagged as not assessed representing epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification partially addresses input uncertainty but scope is insufficient. Overall credibility package does not meet minimum requirements for regulatory submission under ASME V&V 40-2018 at Model Risk Level 5.",
